WEBVTT

00:02.654 --> 00:03.655
Previously onDynasty...Heidi?

00:03.699 --> 00:04.874
"I'm sorry, but it's your turn

00:04.917 --> 00:06.180
to be the parent now."

00:06.223 --> 00:08.356
ADAM:
I poisoned Jeff Colby,

00:08.399 --> 00:10.880
and I did so at the request
of my father.

00:10.923 --> 00:13.013
JENNINGS:
The fire department cleaned up
and left the scene.

00:13.056 --> 00:14.666
It's being reported
as an accident.

00:14.710 --> 00:16.581
They won't find anything
that can lead them back to us.

00:16.625 --> 00:18.061
VANESSA:
After all of that crap

00:18.105 --> 00:20.107
about how you thought of me
as your own child,

00:20.150 --> 00:22.022
you go and screw my boyfriend?!

00:22.065 --> 00:23.371
With all that publicity,

00:23.414 --> 00:27.114
I was able to sell House of Deveraux.

00:33.337 --> 00:35.296
Good morning.

00:35.339 --> 00:37.080
It was.Vanessa, come on.

00:37.124 --> 00:39.082
You can't avoid me forever.

00:39.126 --> 00:40.257
It's a big house.

00:40.301 --> 00:41.737
I know I made a mistake.

00:43.826 --> 00:46.829
Calling someone the wrong name
is a mistake.

00:46.872 --> 00:48.744
You slept withmy boyfriend.

00:48.787 --> 00:50.920
You taped it, and
you released it.

00:50.963 --> 00:53.096
I told you, we were drunk.

00:53.140 --> 00:54.837
It was bad judgment.

00:54.880 --> 00:56.752
And I don't even knowhow it got out.

00:56.795 --> 00:58.101
I must have been hacked.

00:58.145 --> 00:59.972
Why would I believe anything
that you say?

01:00.016 --> 01:02.149
After everything
I've done for you?

01:02.192 --> 01:03.802
I got you a record deal,

01:03.846 --> 01:06.153
this roof over your head,
that croissant.

01:06.196 --> 01:08.068
Oh, you want this back?

01:08.111 --> 01:09.504
Here, take it!

01:10.983 --> 01:12.724
BLAKE:
What the hell's
going on here?

01:12.768 --> 01:14.726
WOMAN:
Cut! Can we
take that again?

01:14.770 --> 01:16.815
Just fromthe croissant throw.

01:16.859 --> 01:18.078
Who are you?

01:18.121 --> 01:20.471
This is Abby,
one of the producers of this

01:20.515 --> 01:22.386
documentary project of ours.

01:22.430 --> 01:23.735
We're calling it

01:23.779 --> 01:25.085
House of Deveraux.

01:25.128 --> 01:26.782
What do you think?

01:26.825 --> 01:30.481
I think this is the house
of me, not some movie set.

01:30.525 --> 01:34.094
And I don't want any of
this anywhere near me.

01:37.184 --> 01:39.055
You're in my chair.

01:40.100 --> 01:42.145
Why don't we pick this up later?

01:42.189 --> 01:44.191
Sure.

01:50.197 --> 01:52.155
Sweetheart?

01:52.199 --> 01:53.852
Have you spoken to Michael?

01:53.896 --> 01:55.115
Not since the party.Wait.

01:55.158 --> 01:57.465
Vanessa...

01:57.508 --> 02:00.032
House of Deveraux
is your story.

02:00.076 --> 02:02.513
And that story started
before that tape,

02:02.557 --> 02:04.167
and Michael was a part of it.

02:04.211 --> 02:06.691
The world needs to know that
you had a good relationship.

02:06.735 --> 02:08.693
What do you want me to do?

02:08.737 --> 02:10.695
Reenact my life
before you ruined it?

02:10.739 --> 02:12.697
Pretend that me and
Michael are still together,

02:12.741 --> 02:14.569
that I don't know
you slept with him?

02:14.612 --> 02:16.875
That's my girl.
I knew you'd get it.

02:19.226 --> 02:22.142
And it's only been a day.How far could Heidi have gotten?

02:22.185 --> 02:23.708
Well, I talked
to the detective,

02:23.752 --> 02:26.189
and she hasn't
turned in her rental car.

02:26.233 --> 02:28.104
Which I'm hoping means
she didn't get on a plane.

02:28.148 --> 02:30.193
Or the car is sitting
in some airport parking lot,

02:30.237 --> 02:32.195
and Heidi is on a beach
in Capri.

02:32.239 --> 02:33.936
That lucky bitch.

02:33.979 --> 02:35.155
Well, I hope not.

02:35.198 --> 02:36.939
There's only so long
Connor will believe

02:36.982 --> 02:38.593
his mom's on another
job interview.

02:38.636 --> 02:41.335
Liam?

02:41.378 --> 02:42.771
Can I have some
chicken fingers?

02:42.814 --> 02:45.121
Didn't you just havescrambled eggs

02:45.165 --> 02:47.384
and-and yogurt and,

02:47.428 --> 02:49.778
like, three of the sugar packetsfrom my coffee?

02:49.821 --> 02:50.996
Chicken fingers.

02:51.040 --> 02:51.910
Coming right up, okay?

02:51.954 --> 02:53.825
Do you thinkhe has a tapeworm?

02:53.869 --> 02:57.177
Can you call room service?
Got to go check in with my guy.

02:57.220 --> 02:59.179
Okay, but if your guydoesn't find anything,

02:59.222 --> 03:01.181
we are gonna need a lot morethan room service.

03:01.224 --> 03:03.618
Like a nannyand a really good shrink.

03:03.661 --> 03:05.054
Oh.

03:05.097 --> 03:06.925
Kids are pretty resilient.

03:07.970 --> 03:10.059
The shrink was for me.

03:16.108 --> 03:17.197
Uh-uh.

03:45.312 --> 03:47.270
WOMAN :
Dr. Sherman to 324.

03:47.314 --> 03:49.403
Dr. Sherman to 324.

03:51.753 --> 03:53.755
