05:53.440 --> 05:55.398
MICHAEL:
I understand your concern,

05:55.442 --> 05:58.401
but that tape was made
without my consent

05:58.445 --> 06:00.403
and has nothing to do
with the Atlantix.

06:00.447 --> 06:01.926
Now, I can assure you,

06:01.970 --> 06:04.929
this is stilla family-friendly organization.

06:04.973 --> 06:06.366
Well, y...

06:06.409 --> 06:08.803
I-I hope that you'll reconsider.

06:10.413 --> 06:11.762
Of course.

06:11.806 --> 06:13.373
They won't reconsider.

06:14.591 --> 06:16.463
That's the eighth sponsor
that we've lost.

06:16.506 --> 06:19.379
And there's three moreon hold, but...

06:19.422 --> 06:21.381
you have a visitor.

06:24.471 --> 06:26.821
Vanessa.

06:26.864 --> 06:29.301
I didn't expect
to see you here,

06:29.345 --> 06:31.129
at least not without a weapon.

06:31.173 --> 06:32.304
Oh, I considered it.

06:32.348 --> 06:36.004
I wanted to scream at you,maybe punch you,

06:36.047 --> 06:38.398
until I realized it wouldn'tchange anything that happened.

06:38.441 --> 06:40.443
What's done is done, and...

06:40.487 --> 06:44.404
I just want to move forward.Well, that's incredibly
mature of you.

06:44.447 --> 06:46.188
Well, don't look so surprised.

06:46.231 --> 06:49.278
Look, I don't wantthat tape to define me.

06:49.321 --> 06:52.586
And right now, I have a chance
to tell the rest of my story.

06:52.629 --> 06:56.154
And, like it or not,
you're a part of it.

06:56.198 --> 06:59.331
So, I was hopingthat you could help me?

06:59.375 --> 07:00.768
Well, of course.

07:00.811 --> 07:02.770
I mean, anything I can do.

07:02.813 --> 07:04.772
So, we're actuallyshooting something.

07:04.815 --> 07:07.035
It's kind of a documentary
about my music.

07:07.078 --> 07:09.951
We have a producer,
a camera crew, all of that.

07:09.994 --> 07:12.170
We? You mean Dominique?

07:12.214 --> 07:13.476
She helped put it together.

07:13.520 --> 07:15.783
Why am I not surprised?

07:15.826 --> 07:18.742
Vanessa,
you do not need Dominique

07:18.786 --> 07:20.701
pushing you
into some reality show.

07:20.744 --> 07:22.485
You are smart.

07:22.529 --> 07:24.139
You're talented.

07:24.182 --> 07:26.315
Do you know
how many smart and talented

07:26.358 --> 07:29.231
singer-songwriters there are,
just in Atlanta?

07:29.274 --> 07:30.493
Most of themnever make it,

07:30.537 --> 07:32.060
and I don't want to be
a bartender forever.

07:32.103 --> 07:34.932
Look, I know thatDominique made that tape,

07:34.976 --> 07:37.108
but she didn'tmake it alone.

07:37.152 --> 07:40.198
And you saidyou wanted to make things right.

07:40.982 --> 07:43.375
Of course she didn't.

07:43.419 --> 07:45.421
And of course I do.

07:45.465 --> 07:47.989
I'm not asking you
to be some reality star

07:48.032 --> 07:50.121
or for us to get back together.

07:50.165 --> 07:51.993
I'm just asking for one day

07:52.036 --> 07:53.951
to pretend
like the tape never happened.

07:53.995 --> 07:55.823
It's the least you could do.

07:57.564 --> 07:59.522
ADAM:
So then he goes, "Well,

07:59.566 --> 08:01.132
at leastI don't have cancer."

08:03.395 --> 08:05.006
I appreciatethe warm welcome.

08:05.049 --> 08:07.095
It's really good to bepracticing medicine again.

08:07.138 --> 08:09.576
Um, speaking of which,I should get back to work.

08:09.619 --> 08:11.752
I'll see you soon.Thanks.

08:13.144 --> 08:16.017
Don't you look handsome
in your white coat.

08:16.060 --> 08:17.584
Mother,what are you doing here?

08:17.627 --> 08:19.281
I didn't know who
else to talk to.

08:19.324 --> 08:21.370
I think Jeff is
getting worse.

08:21.413 --> 08:23.590
This morning at breakfast,
he asked for the salt

08:23.633 --> 08:25.635
instead of the sugar
and didn't even realize it.

08:25.679 --> 08:27.071
Doctor.

08:27.115 --> 08:28.943
It's aphasia. Is it
the first time it's happened?

08:28.986 --> 08:30.379
Well, that I've noticed.

08:30.422 --> 08:32.729
But he's been taking all
these weird herbs and teas.

08:32.773 --> 08:35.123
What kind of herbs?I just told you-- weird.

08:35.166 --> 08:37.081
Well...And they're clearly
not helping.

08:37.125 --> 08:38.692
I don't know what
Blake's new drug company

08:38.735 --> 08:40.302
has been working on,
but whatever it is,

08:40.345 --> 08:41.869
it's got to be
better than this.

08:41.912 --> 08:43.348
Okay, what do you want me to do?

08:43.392 --> 08:46.700
Jeff needs a real doctor,
which you are... sort of.

08:46.743 --> 08:48.310
And I don't need
to remind you

08:48.353 --> 08:50.442
that if anything happens to him,the blood is on your hands.

08:50.486 --> 08:52.096
Okay, okay, let's notget too dramatic,

08:52.140 --> 08:54.969
and can you pleasekeep your voice down?Adam, you con...

08:57.058 --> 09:01.192
You confessed to poisoning
him, Adam, on video.

09:01.236 --> 09:04.195
If that gets released,
you will go to jail.

09:04.239 --> 09:06.981
And you'll be left in the cold.Exactly.

09:07.024 --> 09:10.245
We need to get Jeff
better, Dr. Carrington,

09:10.288 --> 09:12.508
or we're all gonna
pay the price.

09:18.253 --> 09:19.602
LIAM:
Hey, I got something.

09:19.646 --> 09:21.212
Me, too. I think it's an ulcer.

09:21.256 --> 09:25.042
Heidi's debit card was used at
a gas station in Montgomery.

09:25.086 --> 09:26.914
What? Alabama?

09:26.957 --> 09:28.132
