tomorrow morning.

09:34.269 --> 09:35.749
Whoa. Whoa, whoa, whoa.

09:35.792 --> 09:37.794
I mean, can't he just, you know,like, bring her back here?

09:37.838 --> 09:39.100
Why do we have to go to Alabama?

09:39.143 --> 09:41.319
To find her.
But, obviously, I...

09:41.363 --> 09:43.887
I can't bring Connor to
look for his runaway mom.

09:43.931 --> 09:45.236
So what are you gonnado with him?

09:45.280 --> 09:46.455
I thought you could
stay here with him.

09:46.498 --> 09:47.761
It won't be more
than a day.

09:47.804 --> 09:50.198
By myself?Have you seen me with that kid?

09:50.241 --> 09:52.200
