09:59.555 --> 10:01.209
because Vanessa's single
comes out tomorrow,

10:01.252 --> 10:03.820
and I'm supposed to go
to the release party.

10:03.864 --> 10:05.605
You're a hero.Okay.

10:05.648 --> 10:07.650
No, no, not on the algae.

10:38.202 --> 10:40.248
Mmm. Wow.

10:40.291 --> 10:42.511
Well, good morning to you, too.

10:42.554 --> 10:46.080
Mm. I like to check
my cardio off early.

10:46.123 --> 10:48.952
Does that mean we get to stayin bed the rest of the day?

10:48.996 --> 10:49.953
Mm.

10:49.997 --> 10:51.563
I wish.

10:51.607 --> 10:53.304
I should really get moving.

10:53.348 --> 10:55.002
I still have to pack.

10:55.045 --> 10:56.699
Pack? For what?

10:56.743 --> 10:58.701
Mexico.

11:00.355 --> 11:03.314
