14:26.691 --> 14:28.476
Hey, hey, hey,
hey! Hey, hey.

14:28.519 --> 14:30.391
I'm a horse.Stop. What are you doing?

14:30.434 --> 14:31.609
Hey. Hey, hey.
Connor.

14:31.653 --> 14:33.568
